fields.name: Order confirmation - UK
fields.subject: Order confirmation with {{Seller_name}} via Amazon
fields.template:
Dear valued customer

Your order with order ID# {{order_id}} for {{Product_title_s}} dispatched earlier today and is on its way to you! 
 Should you encounter any issues with your order please reply to this email and tell us about how we can make it right.

We aim to reply any inquiry within 24h on normal working days.


 
 
Have a wonderful day,
{{Seller_name}}

fields.name: Review request - UK
fields.subject: Review request with {{Seller_name}} via Amazon
fields.template:
Dear valued customer 

You previously ordered {{Product_title_s}}.
We hope you are willing to help guide your peer shoppers on Amazon for their next buying decision. 
Write your review here 
Should you encounter any issues with your order please reply to this email and tell us about how we can make it right.


Have a wonderful day,
{{Seller_name}}
